<view class="page">
  <view class="notice-bar">
    <view class="notice-icon">营业中</view>
    <view class="muted">开业活动全场 88 折，营业时间 {{shop.hours}}，支持配送和到店自提。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card hero">
    <image class="image hero-image" src="{{heroImage}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
    <view class="hero-mask"></view>
    <view class="hero-content">
      <view class="hero-logo-area" bindtap="handleLogoTap">
        <view class="hero-title">{{shop.name}}</view>
        <view class="hero-subtitle">把时间炖进汤里，让每一份外卖都像刚从灶边端出来。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="hero-pills">
        <text class="pill">{{shop.hours}}</text>
        <text class="pill">{{shop.openingDiscountText}}</text>
        <text class="pill">当前可点 {{availableCount}} 款</text>
      </view>
      <view class="hero-actions">
        <view class="btn" bindtap="goTo" data-page="menu">马上点一单</view>
        <view class="btn btn-ghost hero-ghost" bindtap="goTo" data-page="order">查看订单</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="grid-2 quick-grid">
      <view class="quick-item" bindtap="goTo" data-page="menu">
        <view class="icon-circle">点</view>
        <view class="quick-title">开始点单</view>
        <view class="quick-desc">炖汤、面食、套餐都能直接选，不用再手写备注。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="quick-item" bindtap="goTo" data-page="member">
        <view class="icon-circle">享</view>
        <view class="quick-title">会员权益</view>
        <view class="quick-desc">积分抵扣、老客券、充值活动都放在这里。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="quick-item" bindtap="copyAddress">
        <view class="icon-circle">路</view>
        <view class="quick-title">复制地址</view>
        <view class="quick-desc">位置在意库 66 栋，暖心素火锅隔壁。</view>
      </view>
      <view class="quick-item" bindtap="previewQr">
        <view class="icon-circle">联</view>
        <view class="quick-title">联系店长</view>
        <view class="quick-desc">售后、改单、咨询配送都可以直接扫码联系。</view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title">怎么找到我们</view>
      <view class="tag">意库 66 栋</view>
    </view>
    <image class="image route-preview" src="{{routeImage}}" mode="widthFix" bindtap="previewRoute"></image>
    <view class="muted mt-16">按路线图往前直走，暖心素火锅旁边就是店门口。点开图片可以放大查看。</view>
    <view class="muted mt-8">地址：{{shop.address}}</view>
    <view class="grid-2 mt-20">
      <view class="btn btn-ghost" bindtap="copyAddress">复制地址</view>
      <view class="btn" bindtap="callShop">拨打电话</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-head">
      <view class="section-title">热卖汤品</view>
      <view class="muted">看到喜欢的直接去点单</view>
    </view>
    <scroll-view class="hot-scroll" scroll-x enhanced show-scrollbar="false">
      <view class="hot-list">
        <view wx:for="{{hotSoups}}" wx:key="id" class="hot-card">
          <image class="hot-image" src="{{item.image}}" mode="aspectFill"></image>
          <view class="hot-badge">{{item.hotLabel}}</view>
          <view class="hot-body">
            <view class="hot-name">{{item.name}}</view>
            <view class="muted mt-8 hot-desc">{{item.desc}}</view>
            <view class="row space-between mt-16 align-start">
              <view>
                <view class="price">¥{{item.salePriceText}}</view>
                <view class="muted mt-8">原价 ¥{{item.originalText}}</view>
              </view>
              <view class="stock-note">{{item.stock}} 份可点</view>
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </scroll-view>
    <view class="btn mt-20" bindtap="goTo" data-page="menu">去点单</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card">
    <view class="section-title">店里想传达的感觉</view>
    <view wx:for="{{featuredCards}}" wx:key="title" class="soft-panel feature-card">
      <view class="feature-label">{{item.title}}</view>
      <view class="muted mt-8">{{item.desc}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="mask" wx:if="{{showOwnerModal}}" bindtap="closeOwnerModal"></view>
  <view class="owner-modal" wx:if="{{showOwnerModal}}">
    <view class="owner-title">店长验证</view>
    <view class="muted mt-12">请输入店长密码后进入后台。</view>
    <input
      class="input owner-input"
      password
      value="{{ownerCode}}"
      bindinput="bindOwnerCode"
      placeholder="请输入密码"
      placeholder-class="field-placeholder"
    />
    <view class="owner-actions">
      <view class="btn btn-ghost" bindtap="closeOwnerModal">取消</view>
      <view class="btn" bindtap="confirmOwnerAccess">进入后台</view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
